{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund an integrated program: Sleeping pods for the Homeless by the Homeless",
        "additional_details": "We believe this would:\r\n- Provide safe shelter for thousands.\r\n- Create new jobs for vulnerable people\r\n- Improve quality of life and pathways to independence\r\n- Improve social stability, health, security, and dignity of people facing difficulties\r\n- Turn passive benefit recipients into active contributors to society\r\n\r\nWe believe this program not only humanizes the response to homelessness but offers a smart, sustainable solution that benefits individuals, communities, and the government alike.\r\n",
        "background": "We want the government to:\r\n1. Adopt a national policy for providing secure, clean sleeping pods for any homeless individuals as a foundational UK right.\r\n2. Establish a new, government-supported program to manufacture these pods which employs homeless individuals in the production processes.",
